Package org.jpedal.objects

Class Summary
PdfAnnots holds data from annotations and provides methods to decode, store and retrieve PdfAnnotations.
PdfFileInformation Added as a repository to store PDF file metadata (both legacy fields and XML metadata) in so that it can be accesed.
PdfFormData Added as a repository to store form data in so that it can be reused.
PdfImageData holds metadata on images extracted from the PDF file.
PdfPageData store data relating to page sizes set in PDF (MediaBox, CropBox, rotation)
